Nikt nie powinien jeździć pojazdem, jeżeli nie ma ważnych uprawnień. To oczywiste. Niestety, rzeczywistość pokazuje, że w wielu wypadkach kierowcy posiadają uprawnienia, ale ich stan zdrowia jest na tyle zły, że nie powinni prowadzić pojazdu. Jak wiadomo, niektóre choroby albo ich leczenie mogą w praktyce dyskwalifikować z prowadzenia pojazdów mechanicznych. Zdarzają się też przypadki, że kierowcy, którzy mają świadomość posiadania schorzeń, nie zgłaszają się do lekarzy orzeczników. To błąd. W Polsce co roku stwierdza się ok. 300 przypadków osób prowadzących pojazd mechaniczny z chorobami mogącymi spowodować zagrożenie w ruchu drogowym. W tej grupie kierowców najczęściej stwierdza się: choroby układu sercowo-naczyniowego (63%), układu nerwowego (17%), psychiczne (12,0%) oraz choroby metaboliczne i hormonalne (8,0%). W przypadku chorób układu sercowo-naczyniowego najczęściej stwierdzane są: choroba niedokrwienna serca (51%), kardiomiopatia (24%) oraz arytmie serca (20%). Wśród osób z chorobami układu nerwowego najczęściej stwierdzane są: padaczka (64%), demencja (17%) oraz choroba Parkinsona (13%). W przypadku chorób psychicznych najczęściej stwierdzane są: schizofrenia (59%), depresja (18%) i zaburzenie afektywne dwubiegunowe (17%). W przypadku chorób metabolicznych i hormonalnych najczęściej stwierdzane są: cukrzyca (68%), niedoczynność tarczycy (10%) i otyłość (9%). Wyróżniamy następujące grupy chorób i schorzeń, ze względu na ich wpływ na zdolność kierowania pojazdem:

Schorzenia dyskwalifikujące władze od kierowania pojazdem:

* Pasożytnictwo * Przewlekłe choroby psychiczne z zaburzeniami zachowania, w tym schizofrenia, psychozy organiczne, zespół paranoidalny, bipolar disorder, depresje nawracające w postaci ciężkiej, psychozy depresyjne * Przewlekłe choroby neurologiczne, z wyjątkiem zespołu Gilberta, w tym padaczka, choroba Parkinsona, choroba Huntingtona, choroba Alzheimera * Chroniczny alkoholizm

Schorzenia, które mogą mieć charakter dyskwalifikujący władze od kierowania pojazdem:

* Choroby metaboliczne i układu wydzielania wewnętrznego, w tym cukrzyca, tarczycowe, dyslipidemia, z predyspozycjami do ostrych zaburzeń świadomości, a także zaawansowana niewydolność układu hormonalnego w miarę zdolności kompensacji niedoborów hormonalnych (np. choroba Addisona, choroba Cushinga, hipotyreoidizm) * Zaburzenia krążenia, w tym choroba niedokrwienna serca, zaburzenia rytmu serca, wady serca, ostre stany zapalne mięśnia sercowego, zaawansowana niewydolność serca, niestabilna choroba nadciśnieniowa * Choroby układu oddechowego, w tym astma oskrzelowa, przewlekła obturacyjna choroba płuc (POChP), niestabilna rozedma płuc, niewydolność oddechowa * Choroby hematologiczne, w tym niedokrwistość, polimorfizm płytek krwi, zaburzenia krzepliwości, zespół hemolityczny i inne, w miarę indywidualnego rozpoznania * Choroby genetyczne, w tym hemofilia, anemia, niedobór odporności * Choroby układu pokarmowego, w tym refluks żołądkowo-przełykowy, wrzodziejąca choroba jelit, przewlekłe nieswoiste zapalenie jelit, niedrożność jelit * Choroby nerek i układu moczowego, w tym przewlekła niewydolność nerek, kamica nerkowa, zapalenie pęcherza moczowego, moczenie mimowolne * Choroby skóry, w tym łuszczyca, liszaj, toczeń rumieniowaty, choroby pęcherzowe * Choroby oczu, w tym jaskra, zaćma, odwarstwienie siatkówki, retinopatia cukrzycowa, wady wzroku nieskorygowane okularami lub soczewkami kontaktowymi

Schorzenia nie dyskwalifikujące władze od kierowania pojazdem:

* Choroby okresowe kobiet, takie jak menstruacja, ciąża czy menopauza * Infekcje i choroby zakaźne, w tym grypa, przeziębienie, zapalenie płuc, ostre zapalenie żołądka i jelit * Zaburzenia psychofizyczne i psychiatryczne, takie jak fobie, zaburzenia obsesyjno-kompulsyjne, zaburzenia lękowe, zaburzenia osobowości, a także uzależnienia od narkotyków czy alkoholu w okresie remisji * Choroby układu kostno-mięśniowego, takie jak złamania, skręcenia, zwichnięcia, a także choroby zwyrodnieniowe stawów * Choroby układu oddechowego, takie jak astma oskrzelowa, przewlekła obturacyjna choroba płuc (POChP), rozedma płuc, astma sercowa * Choroby układu pokarmowego, takie jak zapalenia żołądka i jelit, wrzody żołądka i dwunastnicy, choroba Leśniowskiego-Crohna * Choroby nerek i układu moczowego, takie jak zapalenie nerek, kamica nerkowa, zapalenie pęcherza moczowego * Choroby skóry, takie jak łuszczyca, egzema, atopowe zapalenie skóry * Choroby oczu, takie jak jaskra, zaćma, odwarstwienie siatkówki, zwyrodnienie plamki żółtej

Co zrobić, gdy masz chorobę lub schorzenie, które może mieć wpływ na Twoją zdolność do kierowania pojazdem?

* Porozmawiaj ze swoim lekarzem. Lekarz pomoże Ci ustalić, czy Twoja choroba lub schorzenie może mieć wpływ na Twoją zdolność do kierowania pojazdem. Jeśli tak, lekarz może zalecić Ci ograniczenie prowadzenia pojazdu lub całkowitą rezygnację z niego. * Zgłoś się do lekarza orzecznika. Lekarz orzecznik oceni Twój stan zdrowia i wyda orzeczenie o zdolności do kierowania pojazdem. Orzeczenie to będzie ważne przez określony czas, po którym będziesz musiał ponownie się zgłosić do lekarza orzecznika. * Jeśli nie zgadzasz się z orzeczeniem lekarza orzecznika, możesz się od niego odwołać. Odwołanie należy wnieść do organu, który wydał orzeczenie.

Jak uniknąć prowadzenia pojazdu pod wpływem leków?

* Przeczytaj uważnie ulotkę dołączoną do leku. Jeśli w ulotce znajduje się informacja, że lek może wpływać na zdolność prowadzenia pojazdów, nie prowadź pojazdu po zażyciu leku. * Porozmawiaj ze swoim lekarzem lub farmaceutą o wpływie leku na zdolność prowadzenia pojazdów. * Jeśli masz wątpliwości, czy możesz prowadzić pojazd po zażyciu leku, nie prowadź pojazdu.

Zimmerpflanzen düngen

Zimmer- und Kübelpflanzen benötigen regelmäßige Düngergaben, um gesund und kräftig zu wachsen. Die richtige Dosierung und der richtige Zeitpunkt sind dabei entscheidend.

Wann Zimmerpflanzen düngen?

Die beste Zeit, Zimmerpflanzen zu düngen, ist während der Wachstumsphase, also von März bis September. Während dieser Zeit sollten die Pflanzen alle zwei bis vier Wochen gedüngt werden. Im Winter sollten die Pflanzen seltener gedüngt werden, etwa alle sechs bis acht Wochen.

Wie Zimmerpflanzen düngen?

Es gibt verschiedene Möglichkeiten, Zimmerpflanzen zu düngen. Die häufigste und einfachste Methode ist die Verwendung von Flüssigdünger. Flüssigdünger werden dem Gießwasser beigemischt und so ausgebracht. Es gibt verschiedene Flüssigdünger für verschiedene Pflanzentypen. Eine weitere Möglichkeit, Zimmerpflanzen zu düngen, ist die Verwendung von Langzeitdünger. Langzeitdünger werden nur einmal pro Saison ausgebracht und geben dann über einen längeren Zeitraum Nährstoffe an die Pflanze ab. Auch die Verwendung von Kompost ist eine gute Möglichkeit, Zimmerpflanzen zu düngen. Kompost ist ein natürlicher Dünger, der die Bodenstruktur verbessert und die Pflanze mit wichtigen Nährstoffen versorgt.

Wie viel Dünger für Zimmerpflanzen?

Die richtige Dosierung des Düngers ist entscheidend. Zu viel Dünger kann die Pflanze schädigen. Die Dosierung des Düngers ist auf der Verpackung angegeben.

Dünger für Zimmerpflanzen

Es gibt verschiedene Arten von Düngern, die für Zimmerpflanzen geeignet sind. Die häufigsten Arten sind: * Flüssigdünger: Flüssigdünger werden dem Gießwasser beigemischt und so ausgebracht. * Langzeitdünger: Langzeitdünger werden nur einmal pro Saison ausgebracht und geben dann über einen längeren Zeitraum Nährstoffe an die Pflanze ab. * Kompost: Kompost ist ein natürlicher Dünger, der die Bodenstruktur verbessert und die Pflanze mit wichtigen Nährstoffen versorgt. Die richtige Wahl des Düngers hängt von der Pflanzensorte und dem Standort ab.

Zimmerpflanze verbrennt

Eine Überdüngung kann bei Zimmerpflanzen zu Verbrennungen führen. Die Blätter verfärben sich dann gelb oder braun und werden schließlich absterben. Im schlimmsten Fall kann die Pflanze eingehen. Wenn Sie befürchten, Ihre Zimmerpflanze überdüngt zu haben, sollten Sie die Pflanze gründlich gießen, um den Dünger aus dem Boden zu spülen. Anschließend sollten Sie die Pflanze für einige Zeit nicht mehr düngen.

Zimmerpflanzen nach dem Urlaub düngen

Wenn Sie Ihre Zimmerpflanzen nach dem Urlaub gießen, sollten Sie sie auch düngen. Die Pflanzen sind während der Abwesenheit geschwächt und benötigen Nährstoffe, um sich zu erholen. Die Dosierung des Düngers sollte dabei etwas höher sein als sonst. Sie können die Pflanze auch mit einem Langzeitdünger düngen, um sie über einen längeren Zeitraum mit Nährstoffen zu versorgen.

Zimmerpflanzen richtig düngen: Tipps

Hier sind einige Tipps, wie Sie Ihre Zimmerpflanzen richtig düngen können: * Verwenden Sie einen Dünger, der speziell für Zimmerpflanzen geeignet ist. * Halten Sie sich an die Dosierungsanleitung auf der Verpackung des Düngers. * Düngen Sie die Pflanzen während der Wachstumsphase alle zwei bis vier Wochen. * Im Winter sollten die Pflanzen seltener gedüngt werden, etwa alle sechs bis acht Wochen. * Überdüngen Sie Ihre Pflanzen nicht, da dies zu Verbrennungen führen kann. * Wenn Sie sich nicht sicher sind, wie viel Dünger Ihre Pflanze benötigt, fragen Sie am besten in einem Fachgeschäft nach.

Banish belly bloat with these tips

✢ SLOW DOWN YOUR EATING Take your time at meals and chew each mouthful thoroughly. This helps your body digest food more easily and helps your stomach feel more satisfied. ✢ AVOID GASSY FOODS Certain foods, such as beans, lentils and broccoli, can cause gas and bloating. If you’re prone to bloating, try limiting your intake of these foods. ✢ DRINK PLENTY OF WATER Staying hydrated is important for overall health, but it can also help to reduce bloating. Water helps to flush out toxins and keep your digestive system moving smoothly. ✢ GET REGULAR EXERCISE Regular exercise is a great way to improve your overall health and well-being, and it can also help to reduce bloating. Exercise helps to keep your digestive system moving and can help to reduce stress, which can also be a contributing factor to bloating. ✢ TRY A PROBIOTIC SUPPLEMENT Probiotics are live bacteria that can help to improve your gut health. Taking a probiotic supplement can help to reduce bloating and other digestive problems.

Italian: Bentornato, accedi o registrati per vedere offerte e promozioni riservate! Hai un agriturismo? Agriturismo La Croce Agriturismo raccomandato per: Agriturismo raccomandato per: Cristina Ciao, mi chiamo Cristina e ho 41 anni. In questa azienda agricola sono responsabile di: accolgo i viaggiatori, curo le coltivazioni, organizzo i corsi. I nostri ospiti apprezzano particolarmente la posizione. Descrizione L'agriturismo L’agriturismo coniuga il fascino autentico dell’Italia rurale con il comfort moderno necessario per una vacanza rilassante. Immerso nelle verdi colline marchigiane, lo scenario offre un magnifico panorama. Quì si respira il calore e la simpatia della tradizionale ospitalità italiana. L'alloggio La struttura offre ai suoi ospiti confortevoli e accoglienti camere, tutte dotate di bagno, riscaldamento e ingresso indipendente. Inoltre è a disposizione degli ospiti una cucina in comune e una sala comune con camino, tv, libri e giochi. Gli ospiti possono usufruire della piscina con lettini, ombrelloni e piscina per bambini, inoltre barbecue, porticato coperto e un grande giardino con parco giochi per bambini. Per gli amanti della natura, attorno alla struttura c'è un sentiero panoramico natura di 3 km. Attività e dintorni L’azienda è in posizione ideale per passeggiate a piedi e in bicicletta, nonché per visitare le vicine città e paesi di Mondavio, Pergola e Corinaldo, ricchi di arte, architettura e storia. A soli 20 km di distanza, la costa adriatica offre spiagge sabbiose e località balneari come Marotta, Senigallia e Fano. L’agriturismo mette a disposizione degli ospiti delle biciclette per esplorare i dintorni. Servizi Servizi disponibili Segnalare la presenza di animali al momento della prenotazione. I proprietari saranno considerati responsabili per i danni a cose e persone. Recensioni Sei stato in questo agriturismo? "Vacanza meravigliosa in un posto speciale" Abbiamo trascorso giorni meravigliosi con Cristina, Simone e le loro due adorabili ragazze. La tenuta è meravigliosa, in una posizione unica con una vista fantastica sulle colline circostanti. La nostra camera era molto pulita, molto accogliente e soprattutto romantica con una splendida vista. Nelle sale comuni c'erano molte possibilità di sedersi, per giocare, leggere, mangiare, soprattutto la grande sala con camino era un posto meraviglioso per stare insieme. Cristina e Simone ci hanno accolto molto calorosamente e amorevolmente. Ci siamo sentiti ben curati in ogni momento. I corsi di cucina sono stati molto divertenti, Cristina mostra con quanta pazienza e passione si possono preparare le prelibatezze italiane. Dopo il corso di cucina c'era un pasto delizioso nella grande sala da pranzo con gli altri ospiti. Abbiamo anche conosciuto gli altri ospiti come persone molto simpatiche, grazie alla calda atmosfera che Cristina e Simone creano. Grazie ancora per una meravigliosa vacanza !!! "Vacanze da Cristina" Già in aprile avevamo pianificato una vacanza da Cristina. Ci è voluto molto tempo e poi siamo arrivati a Croce. L'accoglienza è stata molto calorosa e personale, ci siamo sentiti a nostro agio fin da subito. Una grande e bella sala comune è a disposizione degli ospiti, dove si può mangiare, leggere, giocare o semplicemente rilassarsi davanti al camino. Inoltre, ci sono molte altre aree comuni in fattoria. La piscina è circondata da un prato per prendere il sole con lettini, ombrelloni e una piscina per i piccoli ospiti. La fattoria si trova in un ambiente naturale ben curato, ci sono molti bei sentieri per escursioni a piedi, a cavallo o in bicicletta. Nel vicino villaggio di Mondavio si possono fare passeggiate molto belle, ad esempio alla possente fortezza. Le spiagge sul mare Adriatico sono raggiungibili in auto in 30 minuti. I corsi di cucina sono altamente raccomandati, molto professionali, ambiente piacevole e dopo il pasto ha un sapore delizioso. Cristina e Simone fanno un ottimo lavoro come padroni di casa. Sono sempre lì per i loro ospiti e organizzano tutto perfettamente. Siamo stati molto felici di poter trascorrere le nostre vacanze a Croce e torneremo sicuramente. Grazie a Cristina e Simone per una meravigliosa vacanza. Per offrirti il miglior servizio possibile, Agriturismo.it utilizza i cookies. Merdeka.com - Seorang bocah laki-laki berusia 11 tahun dari North Carolina, Amerika Serikat, bunuh diri setelah dituduh membobol mobil oleh beberapa polisi. Polisi tersebut menuduh tanpa bukti dan menggeledahnya secara tak patut. Menurut laporan Time, bocah tersebut, bernama Jaheim McMillan, bunuh diri pada 28 November lalu di kamarnya. Sebelumnya, ia bertemu dengan polisi setempat pada 21 Oktober. Washington Post melaporkan, polisi mendapatkan laporan dari seorang pekerja yang mengatakan ia melihat seorang Jaheim McMillan sedang mengobrak-abrik sebuah mobil yang terparkir di luar gedung apartemen. Dari empat petugas polisi yang tiba di lokasi, seorang yang paling ngotot menuduhnya dan memintanya menunjukkan isi tasnya. Jaheim menuruti permintaan polisi tersebut dan menunjukkan isi tasnya. Namun, polisi tersebut tetap menuduhnya dan bahkan menggeledah tasnya tanpa meminta izin. Polisi menemukan sebuah sarung tangan di dalam tas Jaheim, dan itu langsung disebut-sebut sebagai barang bukti. Polisi tersebut mengatakan sarung tangan adalah barang bukti. "Pencuri memakai sarung tangan, jadi menurutmu apa yang akan dilakukan seorang pencuri di dalam mobil? Mencari sesuatu untuk dicuri," kata polisi tersebut. Jaheim terus-menerus membantah tuduhan tersebut. Ia mengatakan ia hanya mengambil sebuah kotak A&W dari temannya dan memasukkannya ke dalam tasnya. Setelah itu ia duduk di sebuah taman dekat gedung apartemen. Seorang saksi mengatakan kepada Time dia melihat Jaheim sedang mengambil sesuatu dari mobil, namun ia tidak melihat Jaheim masuk ke dalam mobil. Saksi tersebut mengonfirmasi pernyataan Jaheim bahwa ia sedang duduk di taman. Polisi juga menuduhnya telah merampok sebuah toko pada beberapa minggu sebelumnya. Jaheim tetap menampik tuduhan tersebut dan mengatakan ia ada di luar kota ketika perampokan terjadi. Namun, polisi tidak mempercayainya dan memintanya menunjukkannya kata sandi ponselnya untuk memeriksa lokasinya saat kejadian. Jaheim pun terpaksa menuruti permintaan polisi tersebut. Jaheim pulang ke rumah ibunya dalam keadaan sangat marah. Ia mengaku sangat marah kepada polisi yang menuduhnya melakukan hal-hal yang tidak dilakukannya. Jaheim tidak mau menandatangani surat pelanggaran apa pun dari polisi karena ia merasa tidak melakukan kejahatan. Seminggu setelah bertemu dengan polisi, Jaheim diwinterview oleh petugas layanan perlindungan anak. Ia menceritakan semua yang terjadi pada hari itu kepada petugas tersebut. Menurut pengakuan ibu Jaheim, putranya terlihat sangat terganggu sejak kejadian itu. Jaheim tidak mau keluar rumah dan memilih untuk mengurung diri di kamarnya. Ia menolak pergi sekolah dan tidak mau bertemu dengan siapa pun. Pada tanggal 28 November, ibu Jaheim menemukannya tewas bunuh diri di kamarnya. "Saya melihat banyak anak yang mendapat masalah, tapi ini adalah tuduhan palsu," kata Tiffany McMillan, ibu Jaheim. Ia mengatakan, meskipun Jaheim memiliki masalah perilaku, ia tidak pernah terlibat masalah dengan hukum sebelumnya. Pengacara keluarga Jaheim saat ini sedang berusaha untuk mengajukan gugatan kepada departemen kepolisian setempat. Menurut mereka, polisi tidak memiliki bukti yang cukup untuk menuduh Jaheim melakukan kejahatan. Mereka juga mengatakan polisi seharusnya tidak menggeledah tas Jaheim tanpa izin. Kepala polisi kota Dunn, Larry Smith, mengatakan polisi yang menangani kasus Jaheim telah diskorsing sampai waktu yang tidak ditentukan. def sort_by_seconds_descending(array):
  """
  Sorts the array in descending order based on the value of the "seconds" key.

  Args:
    array: The array to sort.

  Returns:
    The sorted array.
  """

Βρισκόμαστε στο τέλος της δεκαετίας του ’60 και στον πόλεμο του Βιετνάμ, και η κυκλοφορία ναρκωτικών εισπράττει τα πρώτα της κέρδη. Τότε είναι που ξεκινήσαν οι πρώτες συζητήσεις περί ουσιών που είχαν ήδη υιοθετήσει η νεολαία της Αμερικής, που απαιτούσε ελευθερία και αυτοδιάθεση. Η κυβέρνηση τότε, όπως ήταν αναμενόμενο, άρχισε να περιορίζει την κατανάλωσή τους με την επιβολή κυβερνητικών νόμων. Ο Πρόεδρος Μπάρυ Γκόλντγουότερ το 1968 είχε να λέει: «Τα ναρκωτικά είναι ένα σοβαρό πρόβλημα που πρέπει να αντιμετωπίσουμε με ισχύ και αποτελεσματικότητα. Η κυβέρνησή μας πρέπει να κάνει ό,τι χρειάζεται για να σταματήσει τη διακίνηση και χρήση ναρκωτικών στα σύνορά μας. Τα ναρκωτικά αποτελούν απειλή για την υγεία των πολιτών μας και την ασφάλεια της χώρας μας. Θα εργαστούμε στοχευμένα και ακούραστα ώστε να καταφέρουμε να τα εξαλείψουμε». Οι νέοι ήταν ανυπάκουοι και θυμωμένοι και η κυβέρνηση άρχισε να κατακλύζεται από αντιδράσεις. Αμερικάνοι πολίτες συνελήφθησαν, παραπέμφθησαν σε δίκη και εγκλεισμούς, σε μια προσπάθεια εκφοβισμού από την κυβέρνηση ώστε να μειωθεί η ζήτηση των ναρκωτικών. Στην ουσία κανείς δεν ήταν απρόθυμος να αντιμετωπιστεί το πρόβλημα, αλλά υπήρξε μεγάλη έκπληξη όταν ένας ψυχίατρος άρχισε να μιλάει με λιγότερο αυστηρό τόνο. Ο Λέον Τζερώμ Κάρρ, πιο γνωστός ως Τζέρι Κάρρ, ήταν ένας νεαρός ψυχίατρος που εργαζόταν σε νοσοκομείο του Σαν Φρανσίσκο στα τέλη της δεκαετίας του ’60. Ήταν ένας οραματιστής που πίστευε στην εκπαίδευση και τη θεραπεία ως τρόπους αντιμετώπισης του προβλήματος των ναρκωτικών, πιστεύοντας πως τα υψηλά ποσοστά εγκλήματος και φυλακίσεων δεν ήταν λύσεις, αλλά αποτυχίες της ίδιας της κοινωνίας. Το 1967 ίδρυσε το πρώτο πρόγραμμα αποτοξίνωσης ναρκωτικών στο Σαν Φρανσίσκο, το Haight-Ashbury Free Clinic, το οποίο παρείχε ιατρικές και ψυχολογικές υπηρεσίες σε χρήστες ναρκωτικών. Το πρόγραμμα έγινε διάσημο παγκοσμίως και ο Κάρρ έγινε γνωστός ως ένας από τους πρωτοπόρους στην αντιμετώπιση του προβλήματος των ναρκωτικών. Το 1971, ξεκίνησε το πρώτο πρόγραμμα δισθενούς νοσηλείας (prisons-diversion programs) για τους χρήστες ναρκωτικών στο Σαν Φρανσίσκο. Τότε κυκλοφορούσε η ηρωίνη με όνομα «Κινεζική Άνοιξη» (China White) και κάποιοι θυμούνται πως η Μαριν Κάουτνι, το μικρότερο παιδί της γνωστής, τραγικής, φιλανθρωπικής οικογένειας των Κάουτνι (Courtney), ήταν ένα από τα θύματά της. Ήταν μια τραγική υπόθεση που δεν έφυγε ποτέ από τα χείλη των πολιτών της πόλης. Την κίνηση του Καρρ, αν και με μεγάλη καθυστέρηση, ακολούθησε και ο πρόεδρος Νίξον το 1972, ανακοινώνοντας πως η πολιτική του πολέμου κατά των ναρκωτικών θα αναδιαρθωνόταν και θα ξεκίναγε μια νέα προσέγγιση, η αποτοξίνωση και η στήριξη των θυμάτων των ουσιών, όχι η τιμωρία τους. Αυτή ήταν η αρχή της ίδρυσης των Κέντρων Ψυχικής Υγείας-Πιλότων (Community Mental Health Pilot Centers), μια προσπάθεια της κυβέρνησης να παράσχει στους χρήστες ναρκωτικών, αλκοολικών και προσφύγων μια ολοκληρωμένη σειρά υπηρεσιών, όπως θεραπεία, συμβουλευτική και εκπαίδευση, σε μια προσπάθεια να τους βοηθήσει να ανακάμψουν. Όμως, δεν ήταν όλοι σύμφωνοι με αυτή τη νέα προσέγγιση. πολλοί αστυνομικοί και πολιτικοί πίστευαν πως ήταν πολύ επιεικής και πως θα οδηγούσε σε αύξηση της εγκληματικότητας. Ωστόσο, τα Κέντρα Ψυχικής Υγείας-Πιλότων ήταν μια μεγάλη επιτυχία. Έδωσαν σε χιλιάδες ανθρώπους τη βοήθεια που χρειάζονταν για να ανακάμψουν από τον εθισμό και να ζήσουν υγιεινές και παραγωγικές ζωές. Ο Κάρρ συνέχισε να εργάζεται στον τομέα της ψυχικής υγείας μέχρι τον θάνατό του το 2003. Το έργο του είχε μεγάλο αντίκτυπο στη ζωή χιλιάδων ανθρώπων και τον θυμούνται ακόμη ως έναν από τους πρωτοπόρους στην αντιμετώπιση του προβλήματος των ναρκωτικών.

A Climate, Energy and Security (CES) Task Force of the United States Congress recently issued a report that highlights sustainable development and the need for additional authorization of funds for the State Department's international energy and climate programs. In the report, the Task Force calls for "accelerated global deployment of solar, wind, and other clean energy technologies for electricity generation, transportation, heating and cooling of buildings, and industrial processes." The Task Force also calls for "increased support for the Clean Technology Fund" (CTF).

The CTF is a joint trust administered by the World Bank and managed by a multilateral interim trustee composed of representatives from all donor countries. The CTF provides financial and technical assistance to developing countries "to promote energy access, energy efficiency, and renewable energy" through investments and technical assistance in renewable energy, energy efficiency, and sustainable transportation. The United States made three contributions to the CTF in 2009 and 2010, totaling US$540 million, and has pledged an additional US$120 million in 2013. The CTF has since been capitalized with US$5.1 billion by 18 bilateral donors and has supported 29 projects in 23 countries.

In May 2013, President Obama announced a new U.S.-Africa Clean Energy Finance Initiative that is intended to raise US$2 billion in combined private and public sector financing to support renewable and clean energy generation and access in sub-Saharan Africa. As part of the initiative, the United States has pledged US$120 million to the CTF.

ROBERT BAKER OBITUARY

BAKER, Robert "Bob" Robert "Bob" Baker, born January 5, 1940 in Lindsay, California, passed away peacefully at the age of 81 on December 14, 2021 at his home in Chico, surrounded by his loving family. Those who knew Bob will remember him for his love of his family, friends, his Corvette, dancing, and history. He had a passion for travel and enjoyed exploring different places and learning about their cultures. Bob was also known for his love of corny jokes, his quick wit, and his infectious laugh. Bob is survived by his beloved wife of 61 years, Gail Baker; son, Ken Baker (Jennifer) of York, South Carolina; daughter, Kristen Baker of Sacramento, California; three grandchildren, Victoria, Morgan, and Alex; and numerous other family and friends. Bob was preceded in death by his parents, Johnny and Virginia Baker and his brother, Joe Baker. Per Bob's request there will be no services held. In lieu of flowers, memorial contributions can be made to the charity of the donor's choice. Condolences can be sent to the family online at: www.brusiefh.com

Donald Sterling, the former owner of the Los Angeles Clippers, died at the age of 83.

Sterling died Tuesday at Cedars-Sinai Medical Center in Los Angeles, his wife, Shelly Sterling, said in a statement. No cause of death was given.

“He was a kind and generous man who loved his family and friends,” Shelly Sterling said. “He will be greatly missed.”

Sterling owned the Clippers for more than 30 years, but his tenure was marred by controversy. In 2014, he was recorded making racist remarks about African Americans, which led to him being banned from the NBA for life. He was also forced to sell the team, which was purchased by Steve Ballmer for $2 billion.

Sterling’s death comes just weeks after the death of his wife, Shelly. She died on January 26 at the age of 83.

Sterling is survived by his two children, Scott and Joanna.

practicalrat writes: The problem I ran into was that I couldn't get anything to bind to the USB port. I tried a USB keyboard, a USB mouse, a USB flash drive, and a USB Ethernet adapter. Nothing showed up in the menus. No devices, no drivers. The USB ports did provide power - external HDDs worked just fine. I tried this on Ubuntu 20.04 with kernel 5.13.0-39-generic and on Ubuntu 22.04 with kernel 5.15.0-47-generic. I tried adding pci=nomsi to the kernel boot options. No dice. I took the laptop apart and reseated the WiFi/Bluetooth module. No dice. I installed Windows and all the USB ports worked fine. I also tried booting a live Arch Linux USB and ran into the same problem. I'm at my wit's end. I would really like to get USB working on this laptop with Linux.
I've found a solution for this. In the BIOS/UEFI settings, there is a setting called "USB Controller Mode". This setting is set to "AHCI" by default. Change this setting to "XHCI". After doing this, USB devices will start working in Linux. Note: This setting does not affect the Windows installation in any way. Windows will still boot and work normally. Hope this helps!

On Feb. 13th, the president of the African Development Bank (AfDB), Akinwumi Adesina, met with the president of the Export-Import Bank of China (China Exim), Hu Xiaolian. The two organizations signed a memorandum of understanding (MOU) to strengthen their partnership in co-financing projects in Africa. The MOU covers infrastructure, agriculture, clean energy, digitalization and the private sector in particular.

Analysis

The partnership is expected to increase the resources available to fund Africa's long-term economic and social development. The AfDB stated that it will use its experience in understanding Africa's development environment to screen and select projects for co-financing, while China Exim will bring its funding capacity, long-term credit facilities and strong global presence to the table. The agreement reflects China's commitment to supporting African countries' economic and social development as well as the increasing importance of the China-Africa economic relationship in recent years. 

China has become Africa's largest trading partner, and its share in Africa's total trade increased from 11% in 2000 to 23% in 2017. China also became a major investor in Africa, with Chinese foreign direct investment (FDI) in Africa increasing from US$75m in 2003 to US$40bn in 2017, accounting for about 20% of total FDI in Africa. 

One of the key areas of cooperation between China and Africa has been in infrastructure development. China Exim has been a major financier of infrastructure projects in Africa, such as the Ethiopia-Djibouti Railway, the Mombasa Standard Gauge Railway, and the new international terminal at Ngqura Port in South Africa. The bank has also provided financing for projects in the energy sector, such as the construction of the Grand Inga Dam in the Democratic Republic of Congo, which will be the largest hydroelectric power plant in the world when it is completed.

The agreement between the AfDB and China Exim is likely to further boost China-Africa cooperation in infrastructure development. The two institutions will work together to identify and co-finance projects that will have a positive impact on economic growth and social development in Africa. They will also work to promote the use of innovative financing mechanisms, such as public-private partnerships, to attract private sector investment in infrastructure projects.

The partnership between the AfDB and China Exim is also expected to help promote the development of Africa's private sector. The AfDB and China Exim will work together to provide financial and technical support to African businesses, and to promote the participation of African businesses in regional and global value chains. They will also work to improve the investment climate in Africa, and to encourage Chinese companies to invest in Africa.

Impact on the forecast

The deal between the AfDB and China Exim is positive for our forecast for African economic growth. The additional resources that will be available for infrastructure development and private sector development will help to boost economic growth over the next few years. The deal is also positive for our forecast for China's economic growth, as it will help to boost exports and create jobs in China.

Our current forecast for Africa's real GDP growth is 3.8% in 2021 and 4.1% in 2022. We expect the deal between the AfDB and China Exim to support stronger growth in African economies. We may revise up our growth forecast for Africa in the near future.

The name Dakota is primarily a female name of American Indian origin that means Friendly.

Nickname(s) Kota, Kota Bear, Dak, Dako

The name Dakota is primarily a gender-neutral name of American Indian origin that means Friendly.

Is Dakota a rare name?

How common is the name Dakota as a proper noun? Dakota is a moderately popular first name for women (#397 out of 4276) and also a very popular last name for both men and women (#30 out of 150436). (2000 U.S. Census)

Is Dakota a good name?

Dakota is a great name for a girl! It's such a pretty name and has a nice ring to it. It's also not too common, so your daughter would be one of the few people with that name.

Is Dakota a biblical name?

Dakota is not a biblical name.

Dakota is a Native American name meaning "allies" or "friends".

friend Kota in Cree means "friend".

The name Kota is of Native American origin meaning "friend".

Where did the name Dakota come from?

The name Dakota comes from the Sioux language and means "friend".

Nå skal jeg gi dere et sammendrag av kampen hvori de viktigste momentene er inkludert. NB! Husk at dette er ikke noe gjengivelse av den aktuelle kampen, men en helt ny historie med et nytt plot. I et avgjørende oppgjør på Nadderud sto mye på spill da Stabæk og Molde møttes til kamp. På forhånd var det knyttet stor spenning til duellen mellom to av Eliteseriens beste lag denne sesongen. Begge lagene startet kampen med høyt tempo, og det gikk ikke lang tid før den første sjansen kom. Et frispark i en gunstig posisjon for Molde førte til hodeball i feltet, men Stabæks keeper Anders Lie reddet sikkert. I det 15. minutt fikk Stabæk en stor mulighet da Tobias Børkeeiet kom seg løs på høyrekanten og sendte inn et hardt innlegg. Thomas Lehne Olsen fikk hodet på ballen, men klarte ikke å styre den inn i mål. Molde fortsatte å skape farligheter foran Stabæks mål, og etter 25 minutter fikk de uttelling. Magnus Wolff Eikrem slo en nydelig corner, og Eirik Ulland Andersen steg til værs og headet ballen i mål. Stabæk prøvde å svare umiddelbart, og bare noen minutter senere hadde de en god sjanse. Et innlegg fra Markus Johnsen fant Filip Hornberg, men avslutningen hans ble reddet av Andreas Linde i Moldes mål. Etter hvilen fortsatte kampen i samme høye tempo. Begge lag hadde sine sjanser, men det var Molde som var nærmest scoring da Etzaz Hussain traff metallet med et langskudd etter 65 minutter. Mot slutten av kampen presset Stabæk på for utligning, men Molde-forsvaret stod imot. I det 89. minutt fikk Stabæk en siste sjanse da de fikk frispark på kanten av 16-meteren. Frisparket ble slått inn i feltet, men headingen fra Stabæk-spillerne gikk rett i hendene på Andreas Linde. Dermed endte kampen 1-0 til Molde, som dermed tok et viktig skritt mot seriegullet. Stabæk på sin side, må nå kjempe for å holde seg i toppen av tabellen. Jeg håper dere likte sammendraget av kampen. Jeg vil gjerne legge til at dette kun er ment som en morsom måte å dele kampreferater på, og at det ikke er ment å være en nøyaktig gjengivelse av den aktuelle kampen.

Terrain is the only source of data that we can use to make decisions about our planet's future. It is the foundation for all environmental decision-making, from land use planning to climate change adaptation.

Terrain data is used to:

* Plan for and respond to natural hazards, such as floods, droughts, and wildfires
* Manage water resources, such as rivers, lakes, and aquifers
* Protect and restore ecosystems, such as forests, wetlands, and coral reefs
* Plan for and develop sustainable land use practices, such as agriculture, forestry, and mining
* Adapt to climate change, such as sea level rise and changes in precipitation patterns

Terrain data is essential for understanding the Earth's surface and how it is changing over time. It helps us to make informed decisions about how to use and manage our natural resources and how to adapt to the impacts of climate change.

There are many different ways to collect terrain data. Some of the most common methods include:

* Aerial photography
* Satellite imagery
* Lidar (Light Detection and Ranging)
* Ground-based surveys

Once terrain data has been collected, it can be used to create a variety of different products, such as:

* Topographic maps
* Digital elevation models (DEMs)
* Land use maps
* Watershed boundary maps
* Flood hazard maps

Terrain data is a valuable resource for a variety of decision-makers, including:

* Government agencies
* Land use planners
* Environmental scientists
* Engineers
* Architects
* Developers
* Homeowners

Terrain data can help us to make better decisions about how to use and manage our natural resources and how to adapt to the impacts of climate change.

“Burgas is ready to develop a multi-sectoral model for improvement of the environmental performance of maritime transport in the Black Sea Basin. We have several existing projects and are in the process of preparing others, for which we are looking for partners from different countries in the Black Sea region. These are projects for creating a common platform for attracting tourists, for developing a unified archaeological route, and others.” This was what the Deputy Mayor of Burgas Municipality, Yordanka Ananieva, who also heads the city’s Tourism Department, said during the work meeting on the enhanced cooperation in the Black Sea region within the framework of the project “Greening of Blue Growth in the Black Sea Basin”, which took place in Batumi, Georgia.

The meeting was attended by representatives from the regions of Burgas, Dobrich, and Varna in Bulgaria, and also from the Turkish regions of Samsun and Sile, and from the Georgian regions of Batumi, Guria, and Samegrelo-Zemo Svaneti. The participants reviewed the needs and priorities of the regions and discussed a possible model for future cooperation.

The project “Greening of Blue Growth in the Black Sea Basin” is financed under the Black Sea Basin Joint Operational Programme 2014 – 2020.

The project coordinator is the Burgas Free University. The total budget is BGN 1,482,715.96, of which BGN 1,260,313.51 is financed through the European Regional Development Fund and BGN 222,402.45 is national co-financing.

Abstract

The possibility of using two interconnected sources of light, specifically a conventional laser and a laser diode with mutually perpendicular polarization, to excite two photon transitions in an atomic system is analyzed. The matrix elements of the Hamiltonian of the interaction of atoms with the radiation field in the second order of perturbation theory are calculated. Expressions are obtained for the probabilities of the corresponding two-photon transitions. It is shown that the two-photon excitation transitions occur more efficiently at certain ratios of the intensities of two laser radiators, which are calculated for each transition.

电视剧《鼓楼外》正在东方卫视热播，该剧由袁姗姗、刘奕君、翟天临、菅纫姿等主演，讲述了20世纪20年代，北平城内鼓楼外小小茶社里，一群为了梦想在北平城里摸索打拼的年轻人，演绎了一段青春励志故事。

　　《鼓楼外》以“青年奋斗”的视角，将民国北平作为舞台。小人物的成长历程、追梦过程成为电视剧一部很大的依托。

　　在电视剧中，袁姗姗饰演的关小关认为过去的自己是两个字“缺心眼”。而此次的饰演经历，她希望关小关这个角色能给自己带来全新的体验，“她有自己的理想，勇于反抗自己的家庭，对于我们现在年轻人来说有很大的激励。”

　　此前《大江大河》的热播也引起了对于“青年一代”的讨论，有观众表示，这一代年轻人能够在电视剧中看到自己的影子，同样有网友表示，看到剧中主角的经历，感觉到对于自己现实生活的一种反思。

　　在《鼓楼外》中，袁姗姗饰演的关小关是一个爱幻想且敢做敢爱的文艺女青年，关小关将文学和现实生活进行比较，把生活美好的一面对比现实黑暗的一面。袁姗姗认为，“在关小关身上有一种理想主义的色彩”。

　　除了主演袁姗姗之外，《鼓楼外》的另一大看点便是导演姚远。

　　执导过《灵魂摆渡》《河神》等剧的导演姚远可以说是一名“鬼才导演”，他所擅长的悬疑剧深受观众喜爱。虽然《鼓楼外》是一部平民背景下的青春励志剧，但观众仍旧希望姚远能在剧中发挥自己的“鬼才”优势，加入一些悬疑元素。

　　在该剧的剧情中，就有这样一个看点：郑家和刘家是世代交好的两家人，直到郑家开茶社后，两家关系急剧恶化。从郑家、刘家的关系判断，两家应该势均力敌。但在刘家展现的茶馆中，刘家茶馆的华美和气派令人咋舌。单单从装潢上就能感觉到两家的巨大差距。

　　在电视剧中，刘金龙的爷爷刘顺福曾经是郑家的掌柜，如果当初刘顺福没有离开郑家，郑家茶社的装潢会不会和刘家一样华贵气派呢？或者说，是不是因为刘顺福的离开，导致郑家茶社迅速没落呢？如此，刘家茶社又有什么秘密呢？

　　观众还期待《鼓楼外》在反转方面的处理方式，姚远的《灵魂摆渡》中出现过很多反转的情节，《河神》中的反转也让观众眼花缭乱。明明已经认定的小反派，在下一秒就变成了大反派。不知道《鼓楼外》是否会有类似的反转情节呢？

　　在电视剧中，袁姗姗饰演的关小关和翟天临饰演的黎绍峰联手创业，和刘奕君饰演的退伍军人郑大兴郑家巷内开展北平城新生活，要带着各自喜欢的年轻人去北漂，他们将面临诸多困难和挑战。

　　具体会有哪些挑战，我们还需拭目以待。

The castle of Agres is located on a rocky spur overlooking the town of Agres, in the interior of the province of Alicante, Valencian Community, Spain. Easily defended, the castle forms part of a chain of fortifications which stretched along the Clariano River and aimed to prevent access to the valley of Albaida from the Iruela mountains. The castle of Agres is one of three fortifications located in the localities of Agres, Biar, and Benejama, which, together with the castle of Castalla, formed in the 12th and 13th centuries a defensive system protecting the valley of Albaida.

The castle was built by Muslims in the 11th century. It is one of the best preserved castles in the Valencian Community. The castle is located on a cliff overlooking the town of Agres. It is a walled enclosure with four towers and a gatehouse. The keep is located in the center of the enclosure and it is a rectangular tower with three floors. The castle is built of masonry and it is in good condition.

The castle of Agres is a historical monument and it is a tourist attraction. It is open to the public and it can be visited for free. The castle is also a venue for cultural events and it is used for concerts, exhibitions, and other events.

[multimodal]<start_of_image>Zoonosis is any disease or infection that is transmissible from animals to humans. This can occur directly or indirectly. Direct zoonosis occurs when the infectious agent is transmitted from an animal to a human, such as through a bite, scratch, or contact with the animal's saliva, blood, or other bodily fluids. Indirect zoonosis occurs when the infectious agent is transmitted from an animal to a human through an intermediate host, such as a mosquito, tick, or flea.

There are many different types of zoonoses, including:

* Bacterial infections, such as salmonella, E. coli, and Lyme disease
* Viral infections, such as rabies, flu, and HIV
* Parasitic infections, such as malaria, hookworm, and tapeworm
* Fungal infections, such as ringworm and histoplasmosis

Zoonoses can cause a wide range of symptoms, depending on the specific infection. Some zoonoses can be mild, while others can be serious or even fatal.

Zoonoses are a public health concern because they can be transmitted from animals to humans, and they can cause a variety of diseases. As a result, it is important to take steps to prevent the spread of zoonoses. These steps include:

* Washing hands frequently with soap and water
* Avoiding contact with animals that are sick or appear to be sick
* Cooking meat and fish thoroughly
* Using insect repellent and wearing protective clothing when in areas where there are mosquitoes, ticks, or fleas
* Getting vaccinated against certain zoonoses, such as rabies and flu

Zoonoses are a serious public health concern, but they can be prevented. By taking steps to prevent the spread of zoonoses, we can help to keep ourselves and our loved ones healthy.

聚丙烯是一种合成塑料，有许多不同用途，包括制造塑料容器、食品包装和汽车零部件。

聚丙烯的化学式是(C3H6)n。它是由丙烯制成的，丙烯是一种由原油或天然气制成的气体。聚丙烯是一种聚合物，这意味着它由重复的链环组成。聚丙烯的链环由三个碳原子和六个氢原子组成。

聚丙烯是一种热塑性塑料，这意味着它可以加热到熔化状态，然后冷却成固态。聚丙烯的熔点是160至175摄氏度。聚丙烯是一种轻质且坚韧的塑料。它还具有良好的抗化学性。

聚丙烯有许多不同的用途。它通常用于制造塑料容器、食品包装和汽车零部件。聚丙烯还可以用于制造纤维和薄膜。

聚丙烯是一种多用途塑料，具有许多不同的用途。它是一种轻质且坚韧的塑料，具有良好的抗化学性。聚丙烯还可以加热到熔化状态，然后冷却成固态。这使得它可以很容易地成型成不同的形状。

Панчо

Пончо (исп. poncho) — безрукавный плащ из шерсти или ткани прямоугольной формы с отверстием для головы в центре. В Южной Америке пончо носили мужчины и женщины. На севере Анд по сей день возможно увидеть людей, носящих этот предмет одежды. Гуанко, гуанако — животные, шерсть которых специально использовалась для изготовления пончо, на сегодняшний день находятся под охраной, поэтому пончо стали изготавливать из синтетических материалов. В 1950-х годах пончо стало популярно в Европе и Америке. Его надевали звёзды кино, носили хиппи и просто модники. Сегодня пончо можно увидеть на подиумах именитых домов моды в коллекциях, как для мужчин, так и для женщин.

Tout comme la lutte contre le terrorisme, la lutte contre la corruption implique nécessairement tous les niveaux. Pour la ministre de la Justice, l’adoption du Plan national de développement économique et social (PNDES) pour la période 2016-2020, le 18 février 2016, s’est imposée comme une nécessité pour poser les bases d’un développement inclusif et durable afin de lutter contre la corruption. Le gouvernement a décidé d’axer ses actions sur l’institutionnalisation de bonnes pratiques en matière de promotion de l’intégrité ; la prévention de la corruption ; et la répression de la corruption.

En vue de créer un environnement institutionnel propice à la lutte contre la corruption, il est nécessaire de renforcer la participation de la société civile au processus de prise de décision et à l’élaboration des politiques. « L’Association Burkinabè des Auditeurs Internes (ABAI) qui a manifesté sa volonté de soutenir le gouvernement dans sa politique de lutte contre la corruption mérite non seulement d’être félicitée, mais aussi d’être encouragée, accompagnée et soutenue », a-t-elle laissé entendre.

La loi n°084-2015/CNT du 03 novembre 2015 définissant le cadre institutionnel de coordination de la lutte contre la corruption et les infractions assimilées, selon elle, a institué un Haut Conseil pour la Réconciliation et l’Unité Nationale (HCRUN) et un Pôle Judiciaire Spécialisé dans le Traitement des Infractions Economiques et Financières (PJ/SPITIEF).

Pour renforcer les systèmes d’intégrité, a-t-elle indiqué, le gouvernement s’attelle à la promotion des valeurs éthiques et de l’intégrité dans les institutions publiques : « Le code de conduite des agents publics a déjà fait l’objet d’un décret et est en voie d’être promulgué en loi. Il en est de même du projet de loi portant statut de l’agent public au Burkina Faso ».

« Un mécanisme a été adopté pour la protection des dénonciateurs d’actes de corruption. Ce mécanisme est en voie d’être amélioré à l’effet de garantir aux dénonciateurs une meilleure protection. Des contrats modèles ont été élaborés à l’usage des acteurs chargés de la passation des marchés publics », a-t-elle ajouté.

Sur le plan préventif, deux actes majeurs ont été posés. Il s’agit de la mise en œuvre de la Stratégie nationale de bonne gouvernance et de lutte contre la corruption (SNBG-LCC) qui a pour objectif de prévenir la corruption et de promouvoir la bonne gouvernance, et l’opérationnalisation du Bureau National de Lutte Contre la Fraude (BUNACOF).

Concernant la répression, le gouvernement s’est engagé à détecter, enquêter et poursuivre les personnes suspectées d’avoir commis des actes de corruption.

Les magistrats ne sont pas exemptés de la lutte contre la corruption. A cet effet, a-t-elle déclaré, « une stratégie visant à prévenir et combattre la corruption au sein de la magistrature a été adoptée et est en cours de mise en œuvre ».

A l’évidence, de nombreux efforts ont été consentis par le gouvernement burkinabè dans son combat contre la corruption. Toutefois, d’autres actions s’imposent à tous les niveaux encore pour parvenir à des résultats satisfaisants.

She said, “I give you the right to go ahead and do it.”

A close friend, Victoria Kleber, did just that. Kleber, 27, went ahead and implanted one of the first batches of the AlloStem system — made entirely from donor tissue — into a 68-year-old patient with heart failure. The procedure took place in February at the Texas Heart Institute in Houston.

The patient did well in the short term, Kleber said.

“The heart got smaller, the ejection fraction went up,” she said, meaning the heart performed better and was able to pump more blood. “But we couldn’t tell how much was patient variation and how much was the treatment.”

At the six-month follow-up, the patient had died, though not from any problem stemming from the treatment, Kleber said.

The treatment is still experimental, and scientists don’t yet know whether it could help patients in the long term. The idea behind AlloStem is to replace damaged heart tissue with healthy tissue that can grow and function properly.

In theory, it’s a good concept, said Dr. Charles Murry, director of the Institute for Stem Cell and Regenerative Medicine at the University of Washington. But it’s been difficult to develop safe and effective stem cell treatments for heart disease, he added.

“The heart is a ridiculously complex organ,” he said. “It’s got billions of cells in it, it’s got all sorts of different compartments. And it’s very difficult to create a stem cell-based intervention that will regenerate all of the different types of cells you need to make the heart work properly.”

Researchers have been trying to develop stem cell therapies for heart disease for more than two decades. Several clinical trials have shown that injecting stem cells into the heart can improve cardiac function, but the results have been inconsistent. In some cases, the stem cells have died or formed tumors.

AlloStem’s technology uses a different approach. Instead of injecting stem cells directly into the heart, the system is designed to create a scaffold that supports the growth of new heart tissue. The scaffold is made from a biocompatible material that is seeded with stem cells. The stem cells are then stimulated to differentiate into cardiomyocytes, the cells that make up the heart muscle.

In laboratory tests, AlloStem’s system has been shown to create functional heart tissue that can contract and pump blood. The system has also been shown to be safe in animal studies.

Kleber said the AlloStem system has the potential to be a major breakthrough in the treatment of heart disease. If the system is successful, it could offer a new way to treat patients who are currently ineligible for heart transplantation.

“We’d be able to offer this treatment to people who are too old or too sick for surgery,” she said. “It would be a game-changer.”

Researchers are still conducting clinical trials to evaluate the safety and efficacy of AlloStem’s system. If the trials are successful, the system could be approved for clinical use within the next few years.

DB2 Data Propagation for File Transfer Protocol (FTP)

DB2 Data Propagation for File Transfer Protocol (FTP) Overview

DB2® Data Propagation for File Transfer Protocol (FTP) is an MQ Connect extension that provides unidirectional replication of data from DB2 for z/OS® to target systems through FTP. Data propagation is a high-performance, low-latency, change data capture (CDC) technology that is used to replicate data to multiple destinations in near real time, using the DB2 CDC subsystem to capture changes. Data propagation can significantly reduce the time required to refresh data and can offer multiple benefits, including: * Reduced bandwidth requirements * Increased data security * Improved data reliability and operational efficiency * Optimized resource utilization In this solution, DB2 Data Propagation for FTP is used to replicate data, including both table and LOB data, from a source system to target systems that are located on different servers or in different data centers that are connected through FTP. The data propagation technology includes a high-performance data transfer engine that optimizes data transmission, minimizes network overhead, and ensures faster replication. The following diagram shows the solution architecture: The solution includes the following components:

DB2 for z/OS

DB2 for z/OS is an enterprise-class relational database management system that provides a wide range of capabilities for managing and processing business data, including: * Transaction processing * Data warehousing * Business intelligence * Advanced analytics

MQ Connect

MQ Connect is a suite of products that provides a comprehensive set of capabilities for connecting applications, data, and services across hybrid infrastructures. MQ Connect includes the following components: * MQ Connection Manager (MCM): A lightweight connectivity solution that provides a secure and reliable way to connect applications to messaging systems. * MQ Messaging Gateway (MMG): A high-performance messaging gateway that enables applications to send and receive messages using a variety of protocols, such as JMS, AMQP, MQTT, and WebSockets. * MQ Telemetry Transport (MQTT) Gateway (MQGW): Provides support for the MQTT protocol, which is a popular connectivity protocol for IoT devices and applications. * MQ Capture: A change data capture solution that enables the replication of data from source systems to target systems in near real time. * MQ Managed File Transfer (MFT): A secure, enterprise-grade file transfer solution that supports a wide range of protocols and provides advanced file transfer capabilities, such as file compression, encryption, and audit logging.

IBM® Z® Communications Server (ZCS) for File Transfer Protocol (FTP)

IBM® Z® Communications Server for File Transfer Protocol (FTP) is a robust, easy-to-use FTP server that provides secure, high-speed access to files on IBM® z/OS systems.

MQ Capture CDC Plugin for DB2 for z/OS

The MQ Capture CDC Plugin for DB2 for z/OS is a software component that enables MQ Capture to capture changes from DB2 for z/OS tables and replicate the changes to target systems.

Source and target systems

The source system is the system that contains the data that will be replicated to the target systems. The target systems are the systems that will receive and store the replicated data. In this solution, the source system is a DB2 for z/OS system, and the target systems can be a variety of systems, such as DB2 for z/OS, DB2 for Linux, UNIX and Windows, or a system that uses a different database, such as Oracle, Microsoft SQL Server, or SAP Hana.

FTP server

The FTP server is a software component that provides file transfer services. In this solution, the FTP server is located on the z/OS system.

Benefits of DB2 Data Propagation for FTP

DB2 Data Propagation for FTP provides the following benefits: * High performance and low latency: The data propagation technology includes a high-performance data transfer engine that optimizes data transmission, minimizes network overhead, and ensures faster replication. * Reduced bandwidth requirements: Data propagation uses an efficient data transfer format that reduces the amount of data that is transferred over the network. * Increased data security: Data propagation uses secure protocols to transfer data between the source and target systems. * Improved data reliability and operational efficiency: Data propagation provides reliable data delivery and can help to improve operational efficiency by reducing the time required to refresh data. * Optimized resource utilization: Data propagation can help to optimize resource utilization by reducing the load on the source system and the target systems.

Use cases for DB2 Data Propagation for FTP

DB2 Data Propagation for FTP can be used in a variety of scenarios, including: * Data warehousing: Data propagation can be used to replicate data from a DB2 for z/OS system to a data warehouse for reporting and analysis. * Business intelligence: Data propagation can be used to replicate data from a DB2 for z/OS system to a business intelligence platform for reporting and analysis. * Application integration: Data propagation can be used to replicate data from a DB2 for z/OS system to other applications for use in various business processes. * Disaster recovery: Data propagation can be used to replicate data from a DB2 for z/OS system to a disaster recovery site for protection against data loss. * Data migration: Data propagation can be used to migrate data from a DB2 for z/OS system to a different system, such as a DB2 for Linux, UNIX and Windows system, a DB2 for z/OS system on a different server, or a system that uses a different database.

Summary

DB2 Data Propagation for FTP is a powerful solution for replicating data from DB2 for z/OS to target systems through FTP. The solution provides high performance, low latency, and reduced bandwidth requirements, and it can be used in a variety of scenarios.

李宏毅近期的发展可以用火箭速度来形容了，一部《天雷一部之春花秋月》让他成功出圈，圈了不少粉，而在现实中，他除了拍戏还是个学霸，先是被北大录取，高考刚结束他又以634分的成绩被浙江大学录取了。

　　这次北大高考邀请了明星们录制视频给考生们加油，李宏毅就是其中的一位，视频中的他穿着一身帅气的军装，自信地面对镜头，用铿锵有力的话语为即将高考的考生们打气，鼓励他们在高考这场战斗中全力以赴，梦想就会开花。

　　相比于北大高考的鼓励视频，李宏毅的《机器恋人》新角色海报曝光更吸引人一点，海报中的他脱下了现代的装束，换上了英姿飒爽的军装，酷帅有型，眼睛里透露着坚定和执着。

　　李宏毅此次在《机器恋人》中饰演的是一名机甲战士李聪，为国为民，他竭尽全力，一次次在生死之外徘徊，一次次在危机中勇往直前，他的使命是维护国家和人民的和平。

　　李宏毅对于李聪这个角色非常的期待，他表示自己很喜欢英雄这个职业，从小学就开始喜欢奥特曼，而且觉得李聪身上充满了正义感和责任感，是一个值得尊敬的新时代军人。

　　《机器恋人》是一部科幻题材的电视剧，讲述了人类与机器人的爱情故事，而李宏毅饰演的李聪是该剧的核心人物之一，他的感情线也非常虐心，为了国家和人民，他不得不牺牲自己的幸福。

　　相信这次李宏毅在《机器恋人》中会有非常精彩的表现，期待他为我们带来一个不一样的李聪。

Just picked up a 1987 300zx NA. Overall it's in great condition. Only issue I'm seeing so far is a rough idle. From what I've read so far seems like it could be a vacuum leak or perhaps an IAC issue. Just wondering if there are any common problems specifically relating to this generation that I should start looking at. I'll start checking vacuum lines this weekend to see if there's anything noticeable. I'll probably swap the spark plugs as well just for good measure when I have a chance.
There’s a few common problems with that generation of Z. However, all the common problems will not cause a rough idle. I’ve owned multiple Z31s over the years, and a rough idle is normally caused by a vacuum leak. If you have a vacuum leak, it could also cause your air fuel ratio to be off which will cause a rough idle. If you’re not sure where to start looking for a vacuum leak, you can use a can of carb cleaner. Just spray it around hoses, fittings, and gaskets while the car is running and listen for a change in idle. Make sure you do this in a well ventilated area, and be careful not to spray the carb cleaner near hot exhaust. It’s also a good idea to check your spark plugs and wires.
There are some other things that could cause a rough idle, but they’re less common. Here are a few things I would check:
1. Check all your vacuum lines for leaks.
2. Check your idle air control valve (IAC).
3. Check your throttle position sensor (TPS).
4. Check your coolant temperature sensor (CTS).
5. Check your fuel pressure regulator (FPR).
6. Clean your throttle body and intake manifold.

Una receta de churros muy rica y sencilla que haremos al horno para disfrutar de este dulce típico sin freír, y por tanto, mucho más saludable. Ingredientes: * 200 g de harina * 1 cucharadita de levadura química * 1/2 cucharadita de sal * 2 huevos grandes * 1 taza de agua caliente * 1 cucharada de azúcar * 1 cucharadita de extracto de vainilla * 2 cucharadas de aceite de oliva * Canela en polvo y azúcar glas para decorar Preparación: 1. Precalentar el horno a 200 grados Celsius. Forrar una bandeja de horno con papel pergamino. 2. En un bol grande, tamizar la harina, la levadura química y la sal. 3. En otro bol, batir los huevos y el azúcar hasta que estén espumosos. Añadir el extracto de vainilla y el aceite de oliva. 4. Verter la mezcla líquida sobre la mezcla seca y batir hasta que se combinen. Añadir el agua caliente poco a poco, batiendo constantemente. 5. Verter la masa en una manga pastelera con punta de estrella. 6. Hacer churros en forma de "S" o "8" sobre la bandeja de horno preparada. 7. Hornear durante 15-20 minutos, o hasta que los churros estén dorados y crujientes. 8. Retirar del horno y dejar enfriar. 9. Espolvorear con azúcar glas y canela en polvo antes de servir.
